  "3092560": {
    "name": "Dragon Spot: Cozy Sandbox",
    "steam_appid": 3092560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个由两个人用爱心打造的小小拥抱游戏。它就像一条温暖的毯子，可以让你裹上半小时，放松身心，重新充电。把它在后台运行，创造属于你自己的温馨小世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏝️ <strong>简单设计与岛屿定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/631eb5814bb388022cd3f8eda5577be3.poster.avif?t=1768244682\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/631eb5814bb388022cd3f8eda5577be3.webm?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/631eb5814bb388022cd3f8eda5577be3.mp4?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>只需几个简单的工具，就能轻松创建美丽的岛屿。根据个人喜好定制环境。打造您的完美龙之天堂。无需任何麻烦！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟 <strong>为您的龙发展一个社区</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/22b4cc4d71ea658e9272e7076238a7c5.poster.avif?t=1768244682\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/22b4cc4d71ea658e9272e7076238a7c5.webm?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/22b4cc4d71ea658e9272e7076238a7c5.mp4?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>建立一个不断发展壮大的定居点，让自己沉浸在这个神奇的世界中。看着居民们充满爱心地饲养他们长牙的宠物，将您的岛屿变成一个生机勃勃、欣欣向荣的社区。随着每一个新家的建成和每一次对龙的关爱，这座小岛都会充满温情和魅力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/ada5d0ff8955ec491f719180acd9f101.poster.avif?t=1768244682\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/ada5d0ff8955ec491f719180acd9f101.webm?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/ada5d0ff8955ec491f719180acd9f101.mp4?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 🧩 <strong>拼图模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含拼图模式，这增加了新的挑战和乐趣！在此模式下，您需要：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照预览图片准确重现岛屿。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造地形并将物体放置在正确的位置。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的生物群系中完成多个关卡，每个关卡都提供独特的挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此模式非常适合喜欢解谜和测试细节关注力的玩家。它还介绍了游戏的核心机制，帮助您掌握基本操作。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏠 <strong>个性化您的岛屿每个角落</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/37641e4a73e5cd52dda98d2cb4ffd365.poster.avif?t=1768244682\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/37641e4a73e5cd52dda98d2cb4ffd365.webm?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092560/extras/37641e4a73e5cd52dda98d2cb4ffd365.mp4?t=1768244682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>您的龙将与帮助您养育它们的人生活在一起。为它们建造一个舒适的居住地吧。<br>移动、旋转和调整房屋大小。随意摆放门窗！更改颜色和材料。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 <strong>无限创意</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragon Spot 不仅仅是一款游戏——它是您创意的平台。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 Steam Workshop 分享您的地图，激励其他玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用拼图模式挑战其他玩家或解决他们的地图。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的岛屿就是您的画布。让您的想象力尽情驰骋！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💖 <strong>完美的放松与灵感来源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您想花一个小时还是整整一天，Dragon Spot 都能提供温和而愉快的体验。没有匆忙，没有压力——只有舒适的氛围和专注于创意的机会。非常适合喜欢建造、装饰和照顾虚拟生物的玩家。</p>",
